[{"time":1775113700981,"name":"green name style","tags":"name","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, luxurious 3D render of a decorative square plaque. The central background is deep emerald green velvet or silk fabric featuring a subtle damask pattern. This field is surrounded by an elaborate, ornate, gold metallic frame with intricate arabesque detailing, giving it a baroque look. Dominating the center are large, three-dimensional characters in highly polished silver chrome calligraphy reading: '[text1]'. Positioned above the text is a smaller, 3D golden crescent moon and five-pointed star symbol. The scene is lit with dramatic, cinematic studio lighting, emphasizing the metallic textures, reflections, and deep shadows against the rich green background.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Central Calligraphy Text\",\"value\":\"سُہیل اَحمد رَضا\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1775113701046.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1775113701046.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775112704093,"name":"name calligraphy","tags":"name","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A luxurious, photorealistic 3D render of a formal square presentation image. The background is a [text4] or embossed leather with subtle damask patterns, creating a dark vignette around the edges. A highly ornate, detailed gold frame with intricate traditional Islamic arabesque patterns surrounds the central area. The frame is thick, reflective, and appears deeply embossed. Centered prominently is large, highly polished 3D Arabic calligraphy in [text2] material, reading: [text1]. The calligraphy style is [text3], rendered with high relief and casting subtle shadows. Above the calligraphy, centered near the top edge, is a small, polished gold crescent moon and star symbol. Cinematic, dramatic studio lighting emphasizes the reflective surfaces of the gold, creating bright specular highlights and deep shadows, giving the overall image a feeling of richness and depth.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Name\\/Calligraphy\",\"value\":\"محمد جنید بغدادی\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Text Color\\/Material\",\"value\":\"Brilliant Gold Metallic\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Text Style\",\"value\":\"Elegant 3D Kufic\\/Thuluth\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Background Color\\/Texture\",\"value\":\"Deep Royal Blue Velvet\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1775112704180.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1775112704180.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775093940944,"name":"admission open","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A highly detailed, photorealistic digital illustration designed as a school admissions poster, framed by an elaborate, decorative brown and gold border. The background features a majestic, historical educational building or university complex with classical architecture, domes, and arches, visible under bright, natural daylight. In the foreground of the background, small students are playing on a lush green lawn. Centrally placed are five illustrated figures (students) wearing black graduation gowns and mortarboards with gold tassels, arranged in two rows (two in front, three behind). They are holding academic books. Educational motifs like globes, pencils, and paper planes float around them.\n\nText Placement:\nTop center, flanked by two circular logos, is the school title: \"[text1]\". Directly beneath this, on a red banner, is: \"[text2]\". The main headline, large, colorful, and stylized with a 3D effect, is placed centrally: \"[text3]\".\n\nSpecific text on books held by the students:\nA student holds a book labeled \"[text4]\" and another labeled \"[text5]\". Another student holds a book labeled \"[text6]\" and another labeled \"[text7]\".\n\nLower right section features a maroon box listing school features, headed by the bold title: \"[text8]\". The features listed below this, each with a corresponding icon, are: \"[text9]\", \"[text10]\", \"[text11]\", and \"[text12]\".\n\nAdditional books are labeled \"[text13]\" and \"[text14]\".\n\nAt the bottom strip, the school name is repeated: \"[text15]\", followed by the address: \"[text16]\", and the contact information: \"[text17]\".\n\nColors: Dominated by browns, terracotta, vibrant greens, white, black, and bright primary colors for the headline text. Cinematic lighting, rich textures, high-resolution image quality.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Main School Title (Urdu)\",\"value\":\"مارننگ سٹار سکول\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Admission Year Text\",\"value\":\"داخلہ برائے سال 2026\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Admission Slogan\",\"value\":\"داخلے جاری ہیں\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Subject on book (Urdu)\",\"value\":\"ریاضی\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Subject on book (English)\",\"value\":\"English\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Subject on book (English)\",\"value\":\"Science\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Subject on book (Urdu)\",\"value\":\"ریاضی\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Features Header\",\"value\":\"بماری امتیازی خصوصیات\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 1 (Qualified Teachers)\",\"value\":\"کوالیفائیڈ اور تجربہ کار اساتذہ\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 2 (Spacious Classrooms)\",\"value\":\"کشادہ اور ہوادار کلاس رومز\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 3 (Modern Lab)\",\"value\":\"جدید با مقصد لیبارٹری\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 4 (Curriculum)\",\"value\":\"آکسفورڈ کا نصاب معیاری تعلیم\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"},{\"label\":\"Subject on book (English)\",\"value\":\"Science\",\"key\":\"[text13]\"},{\"label\":\"Subject on book (Urdu)\",\"value\":\"ریاضی\",\"key\":\"[text14]\"},{\"label\":\"School Name (English and Urdu)\",\"value\":\"Morning Star School مارننگ سٹار سکول\",\"key\":\"[text15]\"},{\"label\":\"Address Text\",\"value\":\"پتہ : مین پوسٹ آفس روڈ\",\"key\":\"[text16]\"},{\"label\":\"Contact Information\\/Website\",\"value\":\"03001234567 | www.morningstarschool.pk\",\"key\":\"[text17]\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1775093941072.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1775093941072.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1775093119427,"name":"facebook profile","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic 3D render in a cinematic, dark studio environment, dominated by deep blue tones and neon blue lighting. A stylized 3D character, wearing a light brown kurta pajama and glasses, is seated centrally on a large, matte blue 3D block bearing the glowing white Facebook 'f' logo. The character has a positive expression and is giving a thumbs-up gesture. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Behind the character is a large, rectangular screen displaying a glowing Facebook profile page interface. The screen has a vibrant blue outline. On the profile page banner area, there is a circular photo placeholder of the same character. Above the cover photo area, the word \"[text1]\" appears in the top left corner of the screen UI. The profile name section in the banner shows \"[text2]\" followed by \"[text3]\". Below the banner, the main profile information is visible: \"[text4]\", and underneath that, \"[text5]\". Below the name, there are navigation tabs: \"[text6]\", \"[text7]\", \"[text8]\", and \"[text9]\". A section header reads \"[text10]\" lower down. Floating around the scene are various 3D design-related icons: a camera icon, a palette icon, and two code bracket icons (< / >). The environment features a wooden floor, a dark rug, and background elements like a small wooden shelf with a camera, and a partial view of a desk setup to the right. Cinematic lighting with strong blue rim lights and soft shadows.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Facebook UI header text\",\"value\":\"facebook\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Name in banner area\",\"value\":\"Ahmed Jehanzeb\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Title in banner area\",\"value\":\"AI Graphic Designer\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Main profile name\",\"value\":\"Ahmed Jehanzeb\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Main profile title\",\"value\":\"AI Graphic Designer\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Navigation tab 1\",\"value\":\"Home\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Navigation tab 2\",\"value\":\"About\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Navigation tab 3\",\"value\":\"Previous\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Navigation tab 4\",\"value\":\"More\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Section header\",\"value\":\"About\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1775093119495.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1775093119495.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1774960492407,"name":"cassette profile","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, detailed flat lay image of a sculpted portrait made entirely from dark brown audio cassette magnetic tape. Use the attached photo for the portrait. Keep the face features consistent. The portrait, centered on a light gray or white painted wood background with visible subtle grain texture, depicts a stylized human head and neck with a smiling expression, utilizing the coiled and looping tape similar to a paper quilling technique to create facial contours, hair, and features. A standard audio cassette tape, dark gray/black, is positioned in the lower right corner, connected to the neck area of the portrait by a loose strand of magnetic tape unspooling from it. The cassette label contains the text: [text1]. Cinematic studio lighting creates depth and strong shadows beneath the tape loops and the cassette object, highlighting the three-dimensional relief texture of the artwork. Overhead perspective, high detail.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Name on cassette label\",\"value\":\"ALI MAQBOOL\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1774960492471.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1774960492471.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1774951213934,"name":"madrassa admission","tags":"school, islam","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A highly ornate and formal Islamic promotional flyer design, vertically oriented, utilizing a rich color palette of deep sapphire blue, metallic gold, and antique cream. The background features a large, faded, and highly illuminated photorealistic image of a grand Ottoman-style mosque with multiple domes and towering minarets, positioned centrally in the lower half. Soft golden light emanates from behind the mosque's structure, giving it a celestial glow. The flyer's border is intricate gold foil framing over a cream textured background, with dark teal, patterned corner elements adorned with hanging gold geometric ornaments. The design style is photorealistic with vector graphic overlays (image style). The text is layered prominently in black and deep blue Arabic/Urdu script, styled formally.\n\nTop center, aligned small: \"[text1]\".\nBelow that, in large deep blue script, centered: \"[text2]\".\nBelow that, centered: \"[text3]\".\nBelow that, in very large, bold deep blue script: \"[text4]\".\n\nA wide, curved golden banner sits below, containing the text: \"[text5]\".\nBelow this, a second, darker teal/green gradient banner, highly decorative with gold trim, contains the enrollment period text: \"[text6]\".\n\nIn the middle section, spanning the width above the mosque photo, are two adjacent sections:\nLeft section (on a gold banner): Title \"[text7]\". Below the title, three bullet points in black text, centered: \"[text8]\", \"[text9]\", and \"[text10]\".\nRight section (on a gold banner): Title \"[text11]\". Below the title, five bullet points in black text, left-aligned: \"[text12]\", \"[text13]\", \"[text14]\", \"[text15]\", and \"[text16]\".\n\nBelow the list sections, centered above the base of the mosque: Title \"[text17]\".\nBelow this title, two bullet points in black text: \"[text18]\" and \"[text19]\".\n\nAt the very bottom, a gold-trimmed teal banner/footer element holds the contact information.\nAbove the footer, small text: \"[text20]\".\nCentered in the footer, large, bold contact numbers: \"[text21]\".\n\nPhotorealistic style, cinematic lighting, high detail, traditional Urdu/Arabic calligraphy fonts.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Bismillah calligraphy (Top blessing)\",\"value\":\"بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Institute Name (Main Title)\",\"value\":\"مدرسه اشاعت التوحید\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Location\\/Address\",\"value\":\"تحصیل و ضلع سیالکوٹ\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Admission Announcement Title\",\"value\":\"اعلان داخله\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Admission Status Slogan (Banner 1)\",\"value\":\"داخلہ جاری ہے ! ابتدائی درجات کی معیاری درسگاہ میں داخلے شروع\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Deadline\\/Seat Limit (Banner 2)\",\"value\":\"نشستیں محدود : 10 تا 20 شوال المکرم تک\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Department\\/Programs Title (Left Column)\",\"value\":\"شعبہ جات\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Department 1\",\"value\":\"• شعبه حفظ و ناظره\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Department 2\",\"value\":\"• شعبه تجوید\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Department 3\",\"value\":\"• درجه اولی، اعداد یه و متوسطه\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Features\\/Highlights Title (Right Column)\",\"value\":\"نمایاں خصوصیات\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 1\",\"value\":\"• معیاری تعلیم اور اسلامی تربیت\",\"key\":\"[text12]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 2\",\"value\":\"• نظم وضبط اور روزانہ اسمبلی\",\"key\":\"[text13]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 3\",\"value\":\"• بہترین اخلاق اور ادب کی تعلیم\",\"key\":\"[text14]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 4\",\"value\":\"• عربی، اردو اور دینی تعلیم\",\"key\":\"[text15]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 5\",\"value\":\"• اسکول مضامین کے ساتھ دینی تعلیم\",\"key\":\"[text16]\"},{\"label\":\"Admission Requirements Title\",\"value\":\"شرائط داخله:\",\"key\":\"[text17]\"},{\"label\":\"Requirement 1\",\"value\":\"• مکمل دستاویزات کی فراہمی ضروری\",\"key\":\"[text18]\"},{\"label\":\"Requirement 2\",\"value\":\"• عمر اور جسمانی اہلیت کی جانچ\",\"key\":\"[text19]\"},{\"label\":\"Contact Label\",\"value\":\"رابطه نمبر\",\"key\":\"[text20]\"},{\"label\":\"Phone Numbers (Footer)\",\"value\":\"0347-1234567 | 0321-1234567\",\"key\":\"[text21]\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1774951213984.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1774951213984.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1774948023215,"name":"admission open","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A vector-style educational poster for school admissions. The design is clean with a light blue background featuring a large central illustration of a diverse group of students in graduation gowns holding books. Surrounding the center are flat icons representing science and education: a microscope, a globe, chemical flasks, an atom model, and an open book. At the top, bold, 3D-styled text reads '[text1]'. Below the illustration, a banner titled '[text2]' lists the following points with icons: '[text3]', '[text4]', '[text5]', '[text6]', '[text7]', '[text8]', and '[text9]'. At the bottom, a dark blue footer contains the school name '[text10]', the address '[text11]', and contact information '[text12]' with the website '[text13]'.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Main Title\",\"value\":\"ADMISSION OPEN 2026\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Section Header\",\"value\":\"SALIENT FEATURES\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 1\",\"value\":\"Qualified Staff\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 2\",\"value\":\"Spacious & Well-Ventilated Rooms\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 3\",\"value\":\"Large Playground\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 4\",\"value\":\"Extra Curricular Activities\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 5\",\"value\":\"Purpose Built Campus\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 6\",\"value\":\"Oxford Syllabus\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Feature 7\",\"value\":\"Quality Education\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"School Name\",\"value\":