Sign\",\"value\":\"گورنمنٹ گرلز ہائی سکول فتح پور\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Event Date\",\"value\":\"1 April 2026\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1774947854810.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1774947854810.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1774946425292,"name":"result day","tags":"school","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A highly detailed, photorealistic illustration poster design, vertical orientation, adhering to a traditional Pakistani aesthetic with intricate gold and burgundy decorative borders. Centered at the top, an elaborate gold-trimmed, ornamental burgundy cartouche holds the primary title text \"[text1]\" in large white serif font, followed by \"[text2]\" in large white bold font below it. The upper background is light cream with subtle, faint line art doodles of academic objects. Below the main banner, the large Urdu calligraphy text \"[text3]\" is centrally placed in white. Directly beneath this, a smaller line of Urdu text \"[text4]\" is placed above a dark blue/teal horizontal school signboard. The sign features \"[text5]\" in white capital letters, with \"[text6]\" centered in a smaller white font beneath it, flanked by two circular institutional logos. The main visual composition features a highly detailed illustration of a school entrance with high reddish-brown brick walls and a tall black wrought-iron gate, illuminated by bright daylight. Three figures in matching blue and white school uniforms (shalwar kameez style) are walking directly toward the viewer, holding books, emerging from the gate area. Centered above the figures and overlaid on the illustration, a dark burgundy ribbon banner holds the white invitation text: \"[text7]\". Centered near the bottom, an ornate, gold-rimmed horizontal oval badge contains the final date text: \"[text8]\" in bold black font. Highly detailed digital painting style, photorealistic textures, rich color palette.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Main Title Part 1\",\"value\":\"Annual Result\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Title Part 2 (Year)\",\"value\":\"2026\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Urdu School Name (Large)\",\"value\":\"گورنمنٹ گرلز ہائی سکول فتح پور\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Secondary Urdu School Name (Small)\",\"value\":\"گورنمنٹ گرلز بھائی سکول فخ پور\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"English School Name Part 1\",\"value\":\"GOVERNMENT GIRLS HIGH SCHOOL FATEHĪ\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"English School Name Part 2 (Location)\",\"value\":\"FATEHPUR\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Invitation Slogan\",\"value\":\"We cordially invite all parents and students\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Event Date\",\"value\":\"1 April 2026\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1774946425369.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1774946425369.png","thumbSize":"383,512","type":"image"},{"time":1774854110121,"name":"gift name","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A high-key, photorealistic flat lay arrangement of personalized objects on a pure white background inside a shallow white tray. The central focus is the name \"[text2] [text3]\" rendered in large, glossy 3D block letters with a metallic gold bevel and a deep slate blue face. The text first name  is centered above text second name. Above the text, slightly to the left, is a highly detailed, golden desk crest featuring a wreath encircling a [text1] national emblem. To the upper right of the text are aviator style sunglasses with gold wire frames and amber lenses. To the lower left is a deep green smartphone (iPhone 17 Pro max style) lying face down, partially covering the bottom left corner of the name. To the right of the text is a small, circular enamel lapel pin featuring the same country flag. Below the pin and to the right is a glossy black fountain pen with gold accents. The lighting is soft and bright, creating subtle, defined shadows that emphasize the three-dimensionality of the letters and objects. Luxury product photography aesthetic.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Country Name\",\"value\":\"Pakistan\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"First name in 3D letters\",\"value\":\"Talha\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Last name in 3D letters\",\"value\":\"Mehmood\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"}]","attachment":"dali/img_1774854110190.png","thumb":"dali/thumb_1774854110190.png","thumbSize":"413,512","type":"image"},{"time":1774849430001,"name":"name on glass","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, highly detailed image of a thick, transparent acrylic or glass display plaque standing upright on a glossy, polished white marble desk surface. The plaque features a semi-transparent, vertically oriented portrait photo placeholder of a professional subject in a dark blue suit embedded on the left side. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. The right side of the plaque displays glowing cyan text in a clean, modern sans-serif font. The surface below shows a clear reflection of the plaque, the photo, and the glowing text. Text placement: The first line of text, \"[text1]\", is top-right, followed by the larger text \"[text2]\" directly below it. The job title \"[text3]\" is smaller and centered below the name. Further down, there is a glowing WhatsApp icon followed by the contact information. The line \"[text4]\" precedes the number \"[text5]\". The entire scene is set in a blurred, modern, cool-toned corporate office environment with soft ambient lighting creating a deep bokeh effect. The overall lighting is cinematic and focused on the glowing elements of the glass.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"First name\",\"value\":\"Asif\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Last name\",\"value\":\"Mehmood\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Job title\",\"value\":\"(AI Graphic Designer)\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Contact label prefix\",\"value\":\"WhatsApp:\"},{\"key\":\"[text5]\",\"label\":\"Phone n